* [[血居气球菌|血居气球菌]] ''Aerococcus sanguinicola'' corrig. Lawson et al. 2001
* ''Aerococcus suis'' Vela et al. 2007
* ''Aerococcus urinae'' Aguirre and Collins 1992
* ''Aerococcus urinaeequi'' (Garvie 1988) Felis et al. 2005
* ''Aerococcus urinaehominis'' Lawson et al. 2001
* ''Aerococcus vaginalis'' Tohno et al. 2014
* [[绿色气球菌|绿色气球菌]] ''Aerococcus viridans'' Williams et al. 1953，绿浅气球菌

